  "title": "Sales Support Executive #78039",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Travel Agency</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Sales Support Executive</strong></li><li>Working Location: Bugis (4 mins walking distance from the MRT)</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days (8.30am-5.30pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Manage all operational activities to ensure company growth.</li><li>Generate purchase orders, delivery orders, invoices, and quotations.</li><li>Support sales team with paperwork, allowing them to focus on acquiring new accounts.</li><li>Plan and control inventory, ensuring timely customer payments.</li><li>Mentor new Customer Service Officers to ensure they can handle operational tasks and achieve customer satisfaction.</li><li>Meet deadlines and targets consistently.</li><li>Use the SAP Information System for operational tasks.</li><li>Identify and complete tasks proactively.</li><li>Ensure accuracy and completeness of work and information and follow up to ensure agreements and commitments are met.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum ITE qualification.</li><li>Minimum 1 year of experience in sales support or related field.</li><li>Experienced in service industry is advantageous.</li><li>Excellent communication skills with clients.</li><li>Good time management.</li><li>Able to work in team.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#78039 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
